- Yeah--
- Wait a minute.

1258
01:22:42,657 --> 01:22:45,956
Yeah, but you kids have
to promise not to go there.

1259
01:22:46,027 --> 01:22:47,722
We won't.

1260
01:22:47,796 --> 01:22:50,959
John, on speaker: The audio tone
is coming from Hickory Lake,

1261
01:22:51,032 --> 01:22:53,227
the south shore.

1262
01:22:53,301 --> 01:22:55,701
Okay. We won't go there.

1263
01:22:55,770 --> 01:22:58,671
- Over and out.
- John: Over and out.

1264
01:22:58,740 --> 01:23:01,334
That's not the location.

1265
01:23:01,409 --> 01:23:03,274
I know. But tell them
not to go there,

1266
01:23:03,345 --> 01:23:05,506
and that's where
they'll go for sure.

1267
01:23:05,580 --> 01:23:06,706
You're a genius.

1268
01:23:06,781 --> 01:23:08,544
That's what I've been
trying to tell you.

1269
01:23:11,886 --> 01:23:14,480
The lake isn't in line
with our coordinates.

1270
01:23:14,556 --> 01:23:16,615
It's nowhere near them.

1271
01:23:16,691 --> 01:23:18,488
Well, what else is?

1272
01:23:19,928 --> 01:23:21,589
A Dairy Queen...

1273
01:23:22,664 --> 01:23:23,926
a mountain...

1274
01:23:23,999 --> 01:23:25,660
and the Kramer farm.

1275
01:23:25,734 --> 01:23:28,225
Both:
The Kramer farm!

1276
01:23:31,606 --> 01:23:33,631
( screeching )

1277
01:23:42,150 --> 01:23:44,380
Fuller: Don't worry.
They won't hurt you.

1278
01:23:47,422 --> 01:23:49,447
Not yet.

1279
01:23:49,524 --> 01:23:52,982
My babies won't do a thing...
till they're told.

1280
01:23:53,061 --> 01:23:55,325
And they never let me down.

1281
01:24:01,503 --> 01:24:03,528
Ally: So you have
the coroner's report?

1282
01:24:03,605 --> 01:24:04,902
What does it say?

1283
01:24:04,973 --> 01:24:09,967
The dental records of Arthur Fuller
don't match the body.

1284
01:24:10,045 --> 01:24:12,843
The victim was someone
named Sheldon Broydo?

1285
01:24:12,914 --> 01:24:16,850
Okay, Howard, listen.
Get into evidence lockup.

1286
01:24:16,918 --> 01:24:19,944
But it's locked. That's why
they call it an evidence lockup.

1287
01:24:20,021 --> 01:24:23,286
- You're the only one with a key.
- Ally: Break the lock.

1288
01:24:23,358 --> 01:24:26,850
- And who will pay for that?
- I will. All right?

1289
01:24:26,928 --> 01:24:29,988
Do you remember last year
we seized explosives

1290
01:24:30,065 --> 01:24:33,057
- from that truck on the interstate?
- Uh-huh.

1291
01:24:33,134 --> 01:24:36,103
I need you to get a few pounds
of C-4 and a timer,

1292
01:24:36,171 --> 01:24:37,866
and meet us at the Kramer farm.

1293
