the pressure I did.

1305
01:25:25,920 --> 01:25:27,717
Pressure?!

1306
01:25:27,789 --> 01:25:29,347
It was a trick.

1307
01:25:29,424 --> 01:25:31,790
He thought he had more time
on his loan.

1308
01:25:31,860 --> 01:25:33,794
You gave him 24 hours

1309
01:25:33,862 --> 01:25:35,921
to vacate the only home
he ever knew.

1310
01:25:35,997 --> 01:25:36,929
Hart:
Arthur--

1311
01:25:38,666 --> 01:25:40,657
may I call you Arthur?

1312
01:25:42,303 --> 01:25:46,364
When I foreclosed on your father's
farm, many years ago,

1313
01:25:46,441 --> 01:25:49,069
my partners and I may have...

1314
01:25:51,212 --> 01:25:55,012
falsified certain documents.

1315
01:25:55,083 --> 01:25:58,814
But I'm now willing
to give you a complete refund.

1316
01:26:00,355 --> 01:26:01,913
With interest...

1317
01:26:03,258 --> 01:26:05,351
and no questions asked.

1318
01:26:05,426 --> 01:26:06,552
Stop!

1319
01:26:06,628 --> 01:26:07,652
Stop it!

1320
01:26:09,564 --> 01:26:11,998
The time for deceit is over.

1321
01:26:12,066 --> 01:26:14,296
Hold it right there,
Fuller.

1322
01:26:15,703 --> 01:26:18,035
Put the gun down
or I'll push the button,

1323
01:26:18,106 --> 01:26:20,006
the one that'll end
all our lives.

1324
01:26:20,074 --> 01:26:21,439
You're bluffing.

1325
01:26:21,509 --> 01:26:23,773
Fuller:
You want to call my bluff?

1326
01:26:23,845 --> 01:26:25,836
It's a horrible way to die.

1327
01:26:25,914 --> 01:26:28,280
Yeah, we've seen.

1328
01:26:28,349 --> 01:26:29,907
It's a nice trick...

1329
01:26:29,984 --> 01:26:32,748
faking your own death
to avoid suspicion.

1330
01:26:32,820 --> 01:26:34,412
Thank you.

1331
01:26:35,890 --> 01:26:37,983
And thanks to Mr. Hart...

1332
01:26:38,059 --> 01:26:40,391
Scottsville's
become more urban.

1333
01:26:40,461 --> 01:26:43,055
We have more and more
homeless drifters than ever.

1334
01:26:43,131 --> 01:26:45,395
The body outside your lab.

1335
01:26:45,466 --> 01:26:47,991
One of our drifters
was kind enough to volunteer.

1336
01:26:48,069 --> 01:26:49,969
Volunteer. Yeah, right.

1337
01:26:50,038 --> 01:26:53,474
