are all about? Vengeance?

1338
01:26:53,541 --> 01:26:54,940
Yes.

1339
01:26:55,009 --> 01:26:56,476
Righting a wrong.

1340
01:26:58,413 --> 01:27:02,372
Carl here cheated
my father out of his land

1341
01:27:02,450 --> 01:27:05,476
and built a mini mall
where his farm used to be.

1342
01:27:05,553 --> 01:27:08,818
My father
was left with nothing!

1343
01:27:08,890 --> 01:27:11,222
Now it's time...

1344
01:27:11,292 --> 01:27:13,556
